title: Mulch/Snow Scoop with Fiberglass D-Grip Handle
description: Bully Tools Grain/Snow Scoop is perfect for transfer of all kinds of materials. The reinforced poly head is designed to withstand the elements. It has a High strength triple wall fiberglass handle with a comfort Dgrip handle. The Dgrips have been redesigned for superior comfort and durability. Made with a special no-break Polypropylene co-polymer, you won't find a stronger dgrip. Watch our video to see it crush a cement block. This scoop is able to support more material than you can lift.
